=No. 1 For You Special Edition=

13
00:00:57,690 --> 00:00:58,620
Gao Shi De.

14
00:00:58,890 --> 00:01:00,060
Let's finish this first.

15
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,230
Sorry, I overheard it.

16
