That's why

17
00:01:20,010 --> 00:01:21,140
you tried to avoid me?

18
00:01:25,910 --> 00:01:27,280
You want a girlfriend,

19
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:28,680
right?

20
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,590
I...

21
00:01:36,790 --> 00:01:38,730
I don't want to fall for a man.

22
00:01:49,970 --> 00:01:51,110
Got it.

23
00:02:02,850 --> 00:02:04,120
But you don't have to find a girlfriend

24
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,620
because of this.

25
00:02:06,650 --> 00:02:07,760
It's not fair to the girl.

26
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:11,360
I'm not that odious.

27
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:13,360
Okay, then.

28
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,430
Find a girl you like

29
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:50,670
and be nice to her.

30
00:02:58,140 --> 00:02:59,470
The best way to comfort a broken heart

31
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:01,280
is to fall in love again.

32
00:03:08,580 --> 00:03:09,780
Wish you happy.

33
00:03:11,850 --> 00:03:13,090
Gao Shi De.

34
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,190
See if you can stand up.

35
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,800
Much better.

36
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,270
Thank you.

37
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:32,140
Zhou Shu Yi.

38
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,550
Yes, I like you.

39
00:03:45,150 --> 00:03:46,390
But it's none of your business.

40
00:03:51,390 --> 00:03:52,930
Forget what I said the other day.

41
00:04:25,290 --> 00:04:26,760
Still alive?

42
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:29,760
I thought my son was Le Penseur.

43
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:33,470
What's the matter? Something's bothering you?

44
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,400
Nothing.

45
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,110
Nothing?

46
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:39,170
You're my son.

47
00:04:39,170 --> 00:04:40,940
I know you too well.

48
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:41,910
Don't bother to lie to me.

49
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:43,810
What's the matter?

50
00:04:43,810 --> 00:04:44,610
Just tell me.

51
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:52,550
I was just thinking...

52
00:04:54,820 --> 00:04:56,360
how I can give up someone I like?

53
00:04:59,730 --> 00:05:01,360
Have you tried to pursue that person?

54
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,740
Why would you give up without even trying?

55
00:05:08,170 --> 00:05:10,140
I thought you had guts.

56
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:12,040
I remembered you used to be pretty brave.

57
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:12,970
Did you lost it?

58
00:05:12,970 --> 00:05:14,510
Would you like me to help you find it?

59
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:16,680
Mom.

60
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:19,810
If you like someone,

61
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,380
try as much as you can

62
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:23,250
if nothing stops you from doing it.

63
00:05:23,990 --> 00:05:25,320
If you don't even try,

64
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,120
you won't know how things will turn out.

65
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,790
Without trying,

66
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,990
you must regret it later.

67
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,760
What if

68
00:05:36,030 --> 00:05:38,030
I know I'd fail.

69
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:40,470
Should I still try?

70
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,810
Son.

71
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:45,770
What's wrong with you?

72
00:05:45,770 --> 00:05:47,110
My handsome boy!

73
00:05:48,310 --> 00:05:50,180
Have some confidence, come on!

74
00:05:51,550 --> 00:05:53,350
You're not him.

75
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:55,420
How do you know what he'll say to you?

76
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,690
You should definitely try.

77
00:05:57,690 --> 00:05:59,620
Even if it doesn't work out,

78
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:00,790
so what?

79
00:06:02,090 --> 00:06:04,960
Setbacks will only make a man more attractive.

80
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,100
But you still have to

81
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:09,460
go to America with me.

82
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:10,530
If you choose your lover

83
00:06:10,530 --> 00:06:11,630
over your mother,

84
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:13,100
you're too ungrateful.

85
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:14,400
I won't, Mom.

86
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:15,940
I'll keep my words.

87
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,540
That's good.

88
00:06:17,810 --> 00:06:18,670
Let's eat.

89
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:20,580
I rarely cook.

90
00:06:20,810 --> 00:06:22,780
Yeah. You rarely cook.

91
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:25,950
No work, then.

92
00:06:26,410 --> 00:06:27,980
Enjoy your dinner with your son.

93
00:06:29,650 --> 00:06:31,420
Yes, baby boy.

94
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:32,790
Let's eat.

95
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:37,630
This is your favorite.

96
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:42,960
Eat more and think less.

97
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,070
OK.

98
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,270
There you are!

99
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,780
It smells like talcum powder.

100
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:29,940
Is the shrimp ready?

101
00:07:30,810 --> 00:07:32,250
Yes.

102
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,820
So cool.

103
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:38,890
I thought...

104
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:40,860
you were asking me on a date.

105
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:41,720
I'll take you to the infirmary.

106
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,820
No, thanks.

107
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:45,630
Should I carry you on my back or in my arms?

108
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,630
Choose one.

109
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,930
Zhou Shu Yi.

110
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,270
I like you.

111
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:54,770
None of my business?

112
00:07:55,100 --> 00:07:56,200
You like me.

113
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,710
Of course it's my business.

114
00:08:15,060 --> 00:08:16,920
(Damn idiot)
The deal's off.

115
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,460
I'll delete the video.

116
00:08:18,460 --> 00:08:20,660
Thank you for being my friend these days.

117
00:08:20,660 --> 00:08:22,230
These days?

118
00:08:22,230 --> 00:08:24,430
Did I say I was done with you?

119
00:08:24,730 --> 00:08:26,430
Fine, don't be friends anymore.

120
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:27,640
Who cares!

121
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:49,320
You are crazy about spicy pot, right?

122
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:49,990
Tell you what,

123
00:08:49,990 --> 00:08:51,930
I went to a really great restaurant serving that last week.

124
00:08:51,930 --> 00:08:52,960
Shall we go together?

125
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,330
Invite Gao Shi De to join us.

126
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:56,300
I won't eat with him.

127
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:57,870
Shi De.

128
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:59,730
It's been a long time since we
went out together last time.

129
00:09:00,170 --> 00:09:02,370
Oh, you two had a fight?

130
00:09:02,370 --> 00:09:04,210
That's why I haven't seen you together lately.

131
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:05,870
No.

132
00:09:06,810 --> 00:09:07,880
It's Gao Shi De.

133
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:09,480
What's the matter?

134
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,850
I forgot my phone.

135
00:09:19,950 --> 00:09:20,690
Shu Yi.

136
00:09:20,690 --> 00:09:22,360
The classroom is over there. Where are you going?

137
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,430
Hi!

138
00:09:31,930 --> 00:09:33,370
Do you know what's wrong with them?

139
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:42,010
Mind your own business!

140
00:09:45,510 --> 00:09:46,680
Coward.

141
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:55,490
What's he always this angry lately?

142
00:09:58,260 --> 00:10:00,230
If it hurts, find something to bite on.

143
00:10:00,230 --> 00:10:02,760
Doc, there's no such thing here.

144
00:10:03,830 --> 00:10:05,030
It's done.

145
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:09,140
If you drive fast again,

146
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:11,370
I'll break your bones

147
00:10:11,370 --> 00:10:12,810
before putting plaster on it,

148
00:10:13,310 --> 00:10:16,440
so you'll know the importance of
taking care of your body

149
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:18,710
and won't hurt yourself again.

150
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,880
It's not that we won't.

151
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:22,850
We simply don't dare to.

152
00:10:26,650 --> 00:10:27,660
Get out!

153
00:10:28,190 --> 00:10:29,460
Thank you, school doctor.

154
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,040
Pei Shou Yi.

155
00:10:59,190 --> 00:11:00,550
Miss me?

156
00:11:09,100 --> 00:11:10,600
Pei Shou Yi!

157
00:11:18,610 --> 00:11:19,640
What's the matter?

158
00:11:21,810 --> 00:11:23,240
Nothing.

159
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:25,210
You standing by the door

160
00:11:25,510 --> 00:11:28,150
reminded me of a troublesome kid

161
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:30,020
when I was a high school doctor.

162
00:11:34,660 --> 00:11:36,320
You're done with Mr. Zhou?

163
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,560
Yeah.

164
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:38,730
Right.

165
00:11:39,190 --> 00:11:40,560
Why did you mess with us?

166
00:11:45,770 --> 00:11:47,800
You ate my instant noodles without asking.

167
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,900
Just a bowl of instant noodles.

168
00:11:49,900 --> 00:11:51,210
Seriously?

169
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:57,210
You can eat anything you want,

170
00:11:57,580 --> 00:11:59,450
but not that bag of instant noodles.

171
00:11:59,450 --> 00:12:00,350
That's mine!

172
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,590
If it weren't for you,

173
00:12:06,050 --> 00:12:07,190
we could have been friends

174
00:12:07,190 --> 00:12:08,460
until we graduate.

175
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:12,560
You can't hide your feelings.

176
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:16,560
You have affective disorder,
don't talk about feelings with me.

177
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:19,630
Mind your words.

178
00:12:20,570 --> 00:12:23,000
Where's your easy-going persona?

179
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,570
Busted.

180
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:30,750
I'll save it for you.

181
00:12:32,610 --> 00:12:34,137
♪Wait until tomorrow♪

182
00:12:34,610 --> 00:12:36,672
♪If you also want to♪

183
00:12:36,672 --> 00:12:41,020
♪Change your habit in the rain♪

184
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:45,640
♪The sky and earth are spinning round.
I'm no longer at peace♪

185
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:48,880
♪A call I've never heard♪

186
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:51,580
♪Just woke me up♪

187
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:55,020
♪I just want to hear you say you love me,
over and over again♪

188
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:58,710
♪The aqua blue looks romantic in your eyes♪

189
00:12:58,710 --> 00:13:00,210
Alright, so much for today.

190
00:13:00,210 --> 00:13:02,580
Remember your homework, okay?

191
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,880
OK.

192
00:13:04,530 --> 00:13:07,830
♪Sunlight sprinkles all over the sea♪

193
00:13:07,830 --> 00:13:12,700
♪You're now living in my heart♪

194
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:35,230
♪Like the philosophy in your words♪

195
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:45,040
♪Play the song for the whole day♪

196
00:13:46,470 --> 00:13:49,240
♪Like hiding beside you♪

197
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,240
♪It's just a blink of an eye♪

198
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:56,180
♪Yet you seem to have known me for many years♪

199
00:13:56,180 --> 00:14:00,623
♪How I wish you know♪

200
00:14:00,623 --> 00:14:04,220
♪You don't have to wait till tomorrow♪

201
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:06,020
♪If you also want to♪

202
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:10,530
♪Change your habit in the rain♪

203
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:14,930
♪The sky and earth are spinning round.
I'm no longer at peace♪

204
