207
00:14:29,180 --> 00:14:34,090
♪Maybe the fantasy
will no longer keep me at peace♪

208
00:14:34,090 --> 00:14:37,220
♪Sunlight sprinkles all over the sea♪

209
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:41,630
♪You're now living in my heart♪

210
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,650
I heard the teacher
would talk about the exam questions today.

211
00:14:44,650 --> 00:14:46,050
Do you think it's true?

212
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:49,050
Hey!

213
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:50,990
Hey!

214
00:14:53,450 --> 00:14:55,190
Don't pretend to be strong!

215
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,060
What?

216
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:57,260
Gao Shi De!

217
00:14:57,630 --> 00:14:57,990
Hey!

218
00:14:58,290 --> 00:14:59,060
Why are you hiding from me?

219
00:15:00,330 --> 00:15:01,000
What are you doing?

220
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:02,500
Sorry, man.

221
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:03,760
He thought you were someone else.

222
00:15:05,330 --> 00:15:06,800
What are you doing?

223
00:15:10,300 --> 00:15:11,340
I'm doomed.

224
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:12,410
What?

225
00:15:13,740 --> 00:15:15,280
I think I've fallen for him.

226
00:15:28,220 --> 00:15:29,520
You asked me to come here

227
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:31,160
just to ask me this?

228
00:15:31,160 --> 00:15:32,560
Answer me.

229
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,960
Do you like Zhou Shu Yi?

230
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:37,330
It's none of your business.

231
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,400
Wait!

232
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:40,900
Hear me out.

233
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:41,770
Okay?

234
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:56,650
You know I've liked you for so long.

235
00:15:56,650 --> 00:15:58,590
Do you think it's fun seeing me follow you around?

236
00:16:00,290 --> 00:16:01,460
Shi Zhe Yu.

237
00:16:01,460 --> 00:16:04,060
Don't impose your feelings on others.

238
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:07,090
It is not that you will get anything in return

239
00:16:07,090 --> 00:16:08,560
for your efforts when it comes to love.

240
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,170
Then why didn't you tell me earlier?

241
00:16:18,810 --> 00:16:20,410
If I made you

242
00:16:20,410 --> 00:16:21,540
misunderstand before,

243
00:16:23,580 --> 00:16:24,980
I sincerely apologize for that.

244
00:16:30,350 --> 00:16:31,850
Gao Shi De, you bastard!

245
00:16:32,150 --> 00:16:33,620
How could you do this to me?

246
00:16:33,620 --> 00:16:34,820
Even you're bullying me!

247
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,490
What are you doing?

248
00:16:40,490 --> 00:16:41,960
You've scolded him for long,

249
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:43,330
you must be thirsty.

250
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:45,530
Go away!

251
00:16:45,770 --> 00:16:47,570
I won't accept you.

252
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:51,110
What?

253
00:16:52,710 --> 00:16:53,640
Still pretending?

254
00:16:55,110 --> 00:16:56,680
Every time I teased Zhou Shu Yi,

255
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:58,110
you came and interrupted us.

256
00:16:58,750 --> 00:17:00,950
I know what's on your mind!

257
00:17:01,580 --> 00:17:02,850
You are not my cup of tea!

258
00:17:03,850 --> 00:17:05,090
Of course not.

259
00:17:11,890 --> 00:17:13,390
I don't like you.

260
00:17:13,630 --> 00:17:14,960
I did it for Zhou Shu Yi.

261
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:16,130
Zhou Shu Yi!

262
00:17:16,130 --> 00:17:17,330
Again?

263
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:25,410
Am I that bad?

264
00:17:25,670 --> 00:17:27,040
Why don't you like me even?

265
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:27,920
You're nothing near bad.

266
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,560
-It's just...
-If that's so,

267
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:31,400
How could you not like me?

268
00:17:31,950 --> 00:17:35,560
-Say something! Say it!
-Hey! Control yourself.

269
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:36,950
Tell me!

270
00:17:36,950 --> 00:17:38,360
Say it!

271
00:17:38,360 --> 00:17:40,760
Am I that annoying so no one likes me?

272
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:41,440
Stop it!

273
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:43,920
What aspect about me is bad on earth?

274
00:17:50,130 --> 00:17:51,570
I just don't like you.

275
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:56,200
Are you done?

276
00:18:02,610 --> 00:18:04,950
You can't force people to like you.

277
00:18:11,020 --> 00:18:12,720
You can cry if you want.

278
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:14,190
Bullshit!

279
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:18,830
Smile, then.

280
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,200
Or...

281
00:18:26,130 --> 00:18:28,540
let me buy you dinner.

282
00:18:31,170 --> 00:18:33,170
Good food is for the lovelorn, right?

283
00:18:33,170 --> 00:18:34,740
I'm not lovelorn!

284
00:18:40,410 --> 00:18:42,050
Then let's celebrate the birthday.

285
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:45,720
It's your birthday today?

286
00:18:50,060 --> 00:18:51,390
Yesterday, yeah.

287
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:05,440
If you miss him, go find him.

288
00:19:06,770 --> 00:19:08,710
You think I haven't tried?

289
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:12,480
Then why don't you just ask him out?

290
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:13,910
Why should I?

291
00:19:15,050 --> 00:19:17,650
He'll know I'm looking for him.

292
00:19:18,020 --> 00:19:18,850
It's so embarrassing.

293
00:19:19,850 --> 00:19:21,090
Kiddo.

294
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:23,190
You've been running around school lately

295
00:19:23,190 --> 00:19:24,790
just to meet him, right?

296
00:19:26,130 --> 00:19:26,960
So what?

297
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:31,300
I thought it wasn't so hard to find
someone in the information era.

298
00:19:31,870 --> 00:19:32,970
Now I know

299
00:19:32,970 --> 00:19:35,570
you can never find whoever tries to avoid you.

300
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:38,940
How did he find me before?

301
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:41,180
We're from different departments,

302
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:42,880
but I met him every day.

303
00:19:45,580 --> 00:19:47,410
It occurs to me

304
00:19:47,410 --> 00:19:50,180
he's been there in your whole life.

305
00:19:53,020 --> 00:19:55,520
Do you remember when we played hide and seek?

306
00:19:56,020 --> 00:19:57,290
As long as he was the ghost,

307
00:19:57,290 --> 00:19:59,060
you were always the first to get caught.

308
00:20:01,130 --> 00:20:02,330
Sounds like it.

309
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:08,740
Because he's been watching you.

310
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:12,340
What a stalker!

311
00:20:12,570 --> 00:20:13,440
So creepy.

312
00:20:19,950 --> 00:20:21,950
Zheng Wen told me

313
00:20:21,950 --> 00:20:24,720
you had a crush on me, right?

314
00:20:26,020 --> 00:20:27,150
It's over.

315
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:31,120
But you didn't notice

316
00:20:31,490 --> 00:20:33,190
that Gao Shi De has always been the one

317
00:20:33,190 --> 00:20:34,060
by your side.

318
00:20:36,930 --> 00:20:37,730
Shu Yi.

319
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,500
You've fallen for him, right?

320
00:20:46,340 --> 00:20:47,980
Do what you have to do.

321
00:20:49,180 --> 00:20:50,040
You can make it!

322
00:21:09,300 --> 00:21:11,600
(What are you doing, Gao Shi De?)

323
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:13,500
(I can't find you anywhere.)

324
00:21:18,510 --> 00:21:19,470
Gao Shi De!

325
00:21:20,570 --> 00:21:21,980
You are avoiding me!

326
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:24,380
You're tired of the game?

327
00:21:27,710 --> 00:21:29,020
I deleted the video.

328
00:21:29,020 --> 00:21:30,150
You can check my phone...

329
00:21:31,650 --> 00:21:33,490
You threatened me to be your page boy

330
00:21:33,820 --> 00:21:35,320
with the video

331
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:37,320
because you were worried about me.

332
00:21:41,060 --> 00:21:43,430
You said I could be free if I beat you once

333
00:21:44,770 --> 00:21:46,470
just to distract me.

334
00:21:46,470 --> 00:21:48,140
I'm not that good.

335
00:21:49,140 --> 00:21:50,770
I did it partly for myself, too.

336
00:21:52,910 --> 00:21:54,470
I wanted us to be closer

337
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:56,980
and be friends till graduation.

338
00:21:56,980 --> 00:21:59,150
Aren't you going to tell him?

339
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:10,390
We've just become friends.

340
00:22:10,390 --> 00:22:12,060
I don't want to lose him so soon.

341
00:22:12,930 --> 00:22:14,290
Are you stupid?

342
00:22:14,290 --> 00:22:15,460
Being friends is enough?

343
00:22:15,460 --> 00:22:17,360
You did the same to Jiang Yu Xin
and Fang Zheng Wen.

344
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,570
Well, I gotta go.

345
00:22:26,840 --> 00:22:28,380
Am I still the lucky one?

346
00:22:34,820 --> 00:22:36,820
That day at the infirmary,

347
00:22:36,820 --> 00:22:38,690
I said the one you liked was a lucky guy.

348
00:22:39,820 --> 00:22:41,760
When I was asleep, you said

349
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:43,820
the lucky one had always been me.

350
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:48,200
Is it still me?

351
00:22:50,100 --> 00:22:51,200
Say it!

352
00:22:51,870 --> 00:22:52,830
Is it still me?

353
00:22:54,470 --> 00:22:55,870
It doesn't matter now.

354
00:22:57,770 --> 00:22:59,440
I'm being serious, Gao Shi De.

355
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:00,770
Stop it!

356
00:23:17,860 --> 00:23:18,860
Zhou Shu Yi.

357
00:23:19,890 --> 00:23:21,060
Stop it, or I'll get mad.

358
00:23:21,060 --> 00:23:23,130
I'm the one who should be mad!

359
00:23:23,130 --> 00:23:24,970
So am I still the lucky guy or not?

360
00:23:24,970 --> 00:23:26,630
Or were you just kidding that day?

361
00:23:26,630 --> 00:23:28,240
What the hell are you trying to do?

362
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,840
I like you!

363
00:23:40,150 --> 00:23:42,050
What about Jiang Yu Xin then?

364
00:23:42,050 --> 00:23:43,550
I thought you said you didn't like boys.

365
00:23:43,550 --> 00:23:44,720
Because it's you.

366
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:47,250
I have no choice.

367
00:23:53,830 --> 00:23:55,330
You don't believe me?

368
00:23:55,900 --> 00:23:56,560
OK.

369
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:59,170
What are you doing?

370
00:23:59,830 --> 00:24:00,900
You don't believe me.

371
00:24:00,900 --> 00:24:02,470
I'll prove it to you.

372
00:24:02,470 --> 00:24:04,370
Will you believe me if I throw it away?

373
00:24:05,040 --> 00:24:07,040
It doesn't mean anything.

374
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:12,280
I,

375
00:24:12,280 --> 00:24:16,080
Zhou Shu Yin, like Gao Shi De

376
00:24:16,750 --> 00:24:19,150
very much!

377
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:21,390
I really do!

378
00:24:22,090 --> 00:24:25,990
I love him the most!

379
00:24:26,860 --> 00:24:29,160
I like him so much!

380
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:32,270
I like...

381
00:24:34,940 --> 00:24:36,570
Trust me now?

382
00:24:50,050 --> 00:24:51,850
What's mine is mine.

383
00:24:52,320 --> 00:24:54,190
It'll always be mine.

384
00:24:58,080 --> 00:24:59,480
♪If you also want to♪

385
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:03,780
♪Change your habit in the rain♪

386
00:25:03,780 --> 00:25:08,550
♪The sky and earth are spinning round.
I'm no longer at peace♪

387
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:11,520
♪A call I've never heard♪

388
00:25:11,520 --> 00:25:14,260
♪Just woke me up♪

389
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:17,930
♪I just want to hear you say you love me,
over and over again♪

390
00:25:17,930 --> 00:25:22,600
♪The aqua blue looks romantic in your eyes♪

391
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:27,500
♪Maybe the fantasy
will no longer keep me at peace♪

392
00:25:27,810 --> 00:25:30,640
♪Sunlight sprinkles all over the sea♪

393
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:35,280
♪You're now living in my heart♪

394
00:25:36,560 --> 00:25:38,500
Was that your first kiss?

395
00:25:38,500 --> 00:25:42,391
♪Your breath, your voice♪

396
00:25:42,391 --> 00:25:46,795
♪The closest distance. The utmost quietness♪

397
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:48,810
Who was it?

398
00:25:48,810 --> 00:25:50,810
♪Let there be a sunny rain♪

399
00:25:52,780 --> 00:25:54,350
That day in the swimming pool.

400
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:58,420
That doesn't count.

401
00:26:00,664 --> 00:26:04,840
♪Change some habit in the rain♪

402
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:06,630
♪The sky and earth are spinning round♪

403
00:26:06,630 --> 00:26:08,430
(When you like someone,)

404
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:12,800
(is it his business?)

405
00:26:16,370 --> 00:26:18,870
(Because it's you,)

406
00:26:20,140 --> 00:26:23,380
(I have no choice.)

407
00:26:23,380 --> 00:26:28,537
♪Please don't let the fantasy
simply keep me at peace♪

408
00:26:28,537 --> 00:26:31,573
♪Sunlight sprinkles all over the sea♪

409
00:26:33,890 --> 00:26:37,860
=Lesson 5=
(Because It's You）

410
00:26:50,300 --> 00:26:51,770
(Next episode)
Aren't you nervous with

411
00:26:51,770 --> 00:26:52,740
the one you like?

412
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:55,280
Mama's home, son!

413
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:56,340
I'm so nervous.

414
00:26:56,340 --> 00:26:57,680
Do you mind if I'm with...

415
00:26:57,680 --> 00:26:59,580
Of course, I do.

416
00:26:59,580 --> 00:27:02,480
Young master seems to be in love.

417
00:27:06,050 --> 00:27:07,390
What?

418
00:27:07,390 --> 00:27:08,490
Are you going to the America?

419
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:12,280
♪Only half of it will do♪

420
00:27:12,780 --> 00:27:14,950
♪I don't understand why love♪

421
00:27:14,950 --> 00:27:16,810
♪is always replaced by reality♪

422
00:27:17,210 --> 00:27:23,050
♪I'm waiting at the place
where you left, like a fool♪

423
00:27:23,520 --> 00:27:29,490
♪I never expect♪

424
00:27:29,930 --> 00:27:34,900
♪that letting go is more painful than a breakup♪

425
00:27:34,900 --> 00:27:38,170
♪You're getting further away from me♪

426
00:27:38,170 --> 00:27:40,670
♪Yet I still treasure you in my heart♪

427
00:27:40,670 --> 00:27:43,240
♪I've said goodbye to you♪

428
00:27:43,240 --> 00:27:48,980
♪But I never want you to leave♪

429
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:57,690
♪Forgive me for never knowing♪

430
00:27:58,160 --> 00:28:03,790
♪that letting go is more painful than a breakup♪

431
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:06,130
♪I will no longer be the reason♪

432
00:28:06,130 --> 00:28:08,800
♪for you to be happy or sad♪

433
00:28:08,800 --> 00:28:11,470
♪I've said goodbye to you♪

434
00:28:11,470 --> 00:28:17,570
♪But I'm desperate to make you stay♪
